hopobject.body: Another service? isotretinoin cancer treatment ** Brisbane-based ERM Power Ltd and Australianutility AGL Energy are among the first-round bidders inthe New South Wales government's sale of the state's biggestelectricity generator, people familiar with the process said.The sale of Macquarie Generation, which has a net book value ofsome A$2 billion ($1.93 billion) and accounts for around aquarter of the state's generation capacity, is part of aprivatization program to raise funds for infrastructuredevelopment.
